{
  "name": "RPlog_A_Drink_to_Disaster",
  "title": "A Drink to Disaster",
  "summary": "On the New Alderaan starport of Ord Mantell, the hapless smuggler Jaspar Andromidas lands his Ghtroc freighter Hirakiis and, spotting a marine patrol, makes contact with the New Republic ambassador Ambrosia Delgard by showing off his catalog of curios -- including little figurines of notable figures, among them a scowling one of the Imperial Lord Aldus Thel. Ambrosia takes a wry liking to the smuggler, and the pair ride the Skyline maglev together to the Belleau-a-Lir district and settle into the classy Port of Paradise cantina run by the Duros bartender Yinda. Over drinks, banter, and Ambrosia's fixation on the little Thel figurine, the mood is light until a newscast on the bar's display delivers devastating news that leaves the ambassador frozen, then enraged. She slams her fist down, crushing the glass figurine and shot glass into her bleeding hand, prompting the marines to intervene over the biohazard. Shaken and furious, Ambrosia pays for the damage and storms out, her easy afternoon with Jaspar curdled into disaster.",
